  <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-center">ğŸ“… æˆ‘çš„èª²è¡¨</h1>

  <!-- ç¯€æ¬¡èˆ‡æ™‚é–“è¨­å®šå€ -->
  <div class="mb-6 flex flex-col gap-2">
    <label>ç¯€æ•¸ <input id="numPeriods" type="number" value="7" min="1" class="border p-2 rounded w-full"/></label>
    <label>æ¯ç¯€æ™‚é–“ï¼ˆæ¯è¡Œä¸€ç¯€ï¼Œæ ¼å¼ 8:10-8:50ï¼‰
      <textarea id="periodTimes" class="border p-2 rounded w-full h-32">8:10-8:50
